1.0.0.1.name: connect20/Cymbio_CymbioSearch
1.0.0.1.description:
Cymbio makes your search bar better.
Cymbio turns your no results page to a new opportunity to re-engage users, bring them back to the purchasing funnel, Cymbio improve your search results and allows you to monetize your no results page.
